      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUCKY PAT (1) impressed when successful on debut over 800m at this track. Looks promising, and a top hoop stays aboard. He is well placed to take the next step.  RAGING RAIDER (4) debuts and just missed in a recent Doomben trial with race rider Ben Thompson in the saddle. He's flying, and the filly jumps from the inside gate and can give a bold sight. PROFIT IN PARADISE (2) resumes and has been gelded. Was plain on debut but had won a Gold Coast trial by a space leading into that. Can return much better. SAILING SOLO (3) resumed and has trialled twice. In good hands and keep well PIXIE LANE (5) led and just missed this track/trip first up and then raced flat beaten 3L. She's better than that and should get closer with the extra fitness.",
